title: Episode 187: Butt snaps back (Feat. Shay Johnson)
itunes:title: Episode 187: Butt snaps back (Feat. Shay Johnson)
description:
Love and Hip Hop Miami's Shay Johnson, joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and things get messy when the ladies share stories of the men they've dogged in the past. Shay opens up about her struggles with fibroids and why she wasn't dating during that time. She breaks down why her friendship with Jojo Zarur fell out, her time on Flava Flav's 'Flavor of Love,' and much more. Enjoy!
